subsection.def:
BOC-CC
                    (中銀信用卡公司) means BOC Credit Card
                (International) Limited;

Chiyu
                    (集友) means Chiyu Banking Corporation
                Limited;

existing
                    (現有) means existing, outstanding or in force
                immediately before the appointed time;

Kincheng
                    (金城) means Kincheng Banking Corporation, a
                company incorporated under national law;

Kwangtung
                    (省行) means The Kwangtung Provincial Bank, a
                company incorporated under national law;

def.continued:
to the extent that such business, property and liabilities are governed
                    by Hong Kong law or the transfer of which is governed by Hong Kong law, other
                    than the excluded property and liabilities;

subsection.def:
liabilities
                    (法律責任) includes duties and obligations of
                every description (whether present or future, actual or contingent);

Nanyang
                    (南商) means Nanyang Commercial Bank
                Limited;

will
                    (遺囑) includes a codicil and any other
                testamentary writing;
